Gert-Martin Greuel, Gerhard Pfister, and Hans Schoenemann.

   Contributions to the kernel of SINGULAR have been made by Olaf
Bachmann, Hubert Grassmann, Kai Krueger, Wolfgang Neumann, Thomas
